<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #dc2626;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #fee2e2;
      border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>✗ Batch Rejected by ERTA</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear Administrator,</p>

    <p>We regret to inform you that batch <strong><%= @batch.name %></strong> has been rejected by ERTA.</p>

    <div class="info-box">
      <h3>Batch Details:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Batch Name:</strong> <%= @batch.name %></li>
        <li><strong>Rejection Date:</strong> <%= @rejection_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></li>
        <li><strong>Status:</strong> Rejected</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3>Rejection Reason:</h3>
    <p><%= @rejection_reason %></p>

    <p>Please review the rejection reason and take appropriate action. Students in this batch have been returned to exam-eligible status and may need to be resubmitted after corrections.</p>

    <p>If you have any questions, please contact the system administrator.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>Driving School Management System</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
    <p>&copy; <%= Time.current.year %> Driving School Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
